media.altText:
An iceberg with a list of "social causes of mental illness" under the surface:
Lack of employment 
Social isolation
Punitive welfare system
Racism
Cost of living 
Poor housing
Stigma
Limited access to services

Above the surface is a Mental Health system in crisis:
Understaffed NHS
Police responding to mental health emergencies
Under-resourced mental health social care
